# Trellis — environment configuration.
#
# Without GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY the app still runs end-to-end:
# every skill returns a deterministic stub so the full platform surface
# (persona switcher, policy engine, DLP scanner, audit log, connector
# catalog) is still demonstrable. With the key set, every skill calls
# the Gemini model.
#
# Get a key free from https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# Drop it into Vercel's env UI for deploys, or copy this file to
# .env.local for local dev.

# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=AIza...
